keyAndDialogueList.dialogue: What can I get for you, mate?

I asked you what you 
wanted to drink. Not what 
your job was. Don’t need 
the badge to know you’re a 
bobby.

Oye, now, take it easy, mate, 
no need to get violent. I’d 
put that away if I were you. 
Blokes around here don’t 
take lightly to peelers.

Hmm, can’t say we use 
aprons with the likes of 
these around here. But this 
apron’s made of leather, I 
reckon it’s from somewhere 
down by the docks.

Can’t say that I do, sorry, 
mate. These look like barber 
scissors.
